<reference id="GUID-09957805-70E7-401F-A691-F587FCE2CB8B" xml:lang="en-us">
  <title id="GUID-A4D3FF66-A7CF-4FFC-B107-CCF41F85472A">Widgets for Monitoring
    StellarProtect</title>
  <refbody>
    <section id="GUID-3A481E02-9073-4F55-B437-517CA325F21D">
      <p>Two widgets for monitoring StellarProtect agent events can be added under the
          <uicontrol>Summary</uicontrol> tab of the<uicontrol> Dashboard</uicontrol> screen.<ul
          id="ul_wsg_p2d_n5b">
          <li>
            <p><wintitle>Top Endpoints with Blocked Events</wintitle>: This widget displays the
              endpoints with the most blocked events. By default, the widget is displayed on the
                <uicontrol>Summary</uicontrol> tab of the <uicontrol>Dashboard</uicontrol>.<table
                frame="all" id="table_fhf_s2d_n5b">
                <title>Widget: Top Endpoints with Blocked Events</title>
                <tgroup cols="2">
                  <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                  <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="2.74*"/>
                  <thead>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Column</p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Description</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Endpoint Name</p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Name of the endpoint</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Description </p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Description assigned to the endpoint</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>IP Address </p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>IP address of the endpoint</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Blocked Events</p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Total number of events blocked on the endpoint</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                  </tbody>
                </tgroup>
              </table></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><wintitle>Top Blocked Files</wintitle>: This widget displays a list of files that
              triggered the most blocked events.<table frame="all" id="table_wtn_5fd_n5b">
                <title>Widget: Top Blocked Files</title>
                <tgroup cols="2">
                  <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                  <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="2.71*"/>
                  <thead>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Column</p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Description</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>File Name</p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Name of the file that triggered the blocked events</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>File Hash</p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>SHA1 hash of the file that triggered the blocked events</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Endpoints</p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Total number of the endpoints that reported the blocked events triggered
                          by the file</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Blocked Events</p>
                      </entry>
                      <entry>
                        <p>Total number of the blocked events triggerd by the file</p>
                      </entry>
                    </row>
                  </tbody>
                </tgroup>
              </table></p>
          </li>
        </ul><note id="note_pn1_1fd_n5b" type="tip">
          <p>
            <fig id="fig_kzt_5gd_n5b" otherprops="PRINT">
              <image href="../images/widgetDropDownMenu=20220814005647.png" id="image_z5b_wgd_n5b"
                otherprops="PRINT" scalefit="no" scale="50"/>
            </fig>
            <fig id="fig_jw3_vgd_n5b" otherprops="PRINT">
              <image href="../images/widgetRefrech=20220814005543.png" id="image_lyd_vgd_n5b"
                otherprops="PRINT" scalefit="no" scale="50"/>
            </fig>
            <ul id="ul_ox5_wgd_n5b">
              <li>
                <p>Click the <image href="../images/widgetRefreshIcon=20220814010039.png"
                    id="image_u5p_chd_n5b" scalefit="yes"/> button to start auto refresh. Click the
                    <image href="../images/stopRefreshIcon=20220814010319.png"
                    id="image_avq_lhd_n5b" scalefit="yes"/> button to pause auto refresh.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p>The <image href="../images/widgetDropDownIcon=20220814011647.png"
                    id="image_vyy_fjd_n5b" scalefit="yes"/> dropdown-menu button provides two
                    functions:<ul id="ul_tym_5hd_n5b">
                    <li>
                      <p><uicontrol>Widget Settings</uicontrol>:</p>
                      <ul id="ul_r4h_b3d_n5b">
                        <li>
                          <p><uicontrol>Widget Name</uicontrol>: allows users to edit the name for
                            the widget.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <p><uicontrol>Time Period</uicontrol>: allows users to select a specific
                            timeframe, which determines the number of the blocked events or files to
                            display (The default value is <uicontrol>Last 7 days</uicontrol>).</p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <p><uicontrol>Auto Refresh Settings</uicontrol>: allows users to change
                            the setting to manual refresh or to configure the auto refresh frequency
                            (The default value is <uicontrol>Every 5 minutes</uicontrol>).</p>
                        </li>
                      </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <p><uicontrol>Remove Widget</uicontrol>: allows users to remove the widgets
                        from the <wintitle>Dashboard</wintitle> screen.</p>
                    </li>
                  </ul></p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p>To move a widget, click and hold on the title bar of the widget and drag it to
                  various locations on the tab page.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p>To resize a widget, mouse over the edge of the widget and a diagonal resize
                  pointer appears. Drag it to resize the widget.</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </note></p>
    </section>
  </refbody>
